@startuml
title Bytom Server - Performance & Deployment Sequence Diagram

actor "Node Operator" as Operator
participant "bytomd CLI" as CLI
participant "gRPC API\nApiService" as API
participant "Access Token\nManager" as Auth
participant "Protocol\nReactor" as Protocol
participant "P2P Network\nLayer" as P2P
participant "Block Sync\nnetsync" as Sync
participant "TxPool" as TxPool
participant "Mining Engine\n(Tensority)" as Mining
participant "Bytom VM" as VM
participant "Blockchain\nCore" as Blockchain
participant "State Manager\nUTXO" as State
database "LevelDB\n(dbm.DB)" as DB
participant "Remote Peer\nNode" as Peer

== Node Deployment & Initialization ==
Operator -> CLI: Start bytomd node
activate CLI
CLI -> API: Initialize gRPC Server
activate API
API -> Auth: Setup Access Token Auth
activate Auth
Auth --> API: Auth Ready
deactivate Auth

CLI -> Protocol: Initialize Protocol Reactor
activate Protocol
Protocol -> Blockchain: Load Blockchain State
activate Blockchain
Blockchain -> DB: Query Latest Block
activate DB
DB --> Blockchain: Block Data
deactivate DB
Blockchain --> Protocol: State Loaded
deactivate Blockchain

CLI -> P2P: Start P2P Network Layer
activate P2P
P2P -> P2P: Initialize SecretConnection
P2P --> CLI: P2P Ready
deactivate P2P

CLI -> TxPool: Initialize Transaction Pool
activate TxPool
TxPool -> DB: Load Pending Transactions
activate DB
DB --> TxPool: Transaction Data
deactivate DB
TxPool --> CLI: TxPool Ready
deactivate TxPool

CLI -> Mining: Initialize Mining Engine
activate Mining
Mining --> CLI: Mining Ready
deactivate Mining

CLI --> Operator: Node Deployed & Running
deactivate CLI

== Performance: Block Synchronization ==
Peer -> P2P: BlockRequest Message
activate P2P
P2P -> Protocol: Route BlockRequest
activate Protocol
Protocol -> Sync: Handle Block Sync
activate Sync
Sync -> Blockchain: Get Block at Height
activate Blockchain
Blockchain -> DB: Query Block Data (Optimized)
activate DB
DB --> Blockchain: Block Data
deactivate DB
Blockchain --> Sync: Block Retrieved
deactivate Blockchain
Sync -> Protocol: BlockResponse
deactivate Sync
Protocol -> P2P: Send BlockResponse
deactivate Protocol
P2P -> Peer: BlockResponse Message
deactivate P2P

== Performance: Transaction Processing ==
Operator -> API: Submit Transaction (gRPC)
activate API
API -> Auth: Validate Access Token
activate Auth
Auth --> API: Token Valid
deactivate Auth

API -> TxPool: Add Transaction
activate TxPool
TxPool -> TxPool: Check Double-Spend (Fast)
TxPool -> VM: Validate Transaction Script
activate VM
VM -> VM: Execute Opcodes (Optimized)
VM -> VM: Check Gas Consumption
VM --> TxPool: Validation Result
deactivate VM

TxPool -> State: Verify UTXO Availability
activate State
State -> DB: Query UTXO Set (Indexed)
activate DB
DB --> State: UTXO Data
deactivate DB
State --> TxPool: UTXO Valid
deactivate State

TxPool -> Protocol: Broadcast TransactionNotify
activate Protocol
Protocol -> P2P: Route to Peers
activate P2P
P2P -> Peer: TransactionNotify Message
deactivate P2P
deactivate Protocol

TxPool --> API: Transaction Accepted
deactivate TxPool
API --> Operator: Transaction Confirmed
deactivate API

== Performance: Mining & Block Creation ==
Mining -> Mining: CPU Mining Loop (Tensority PoW)
activate Mining
Mining -> TxPool: Get Pending Transactions
activate TxPool
TxPool --> Mining: Transaction List (Workspace Pool)
deactivate TxPool

Mining -> Mining: Create Block Template
Mining -> Mining: Calculate Tensority Hash (BLAS Optimized)
Mining -> Mining: Find Valid Nonce

Mining -> Protocol: Submit Block
activate Protocol
Protocol -> Blockchain: Validate Block
activate Blockchain
Blockchain -> Blockchain: Verify Consensus Rules
Blockchain -> State: Update UTXO Set
activate State
State -> DB: Batch Write Updates (Performance)
activate DB
DB --> State: Write Complete
deactivate DB
State --> Blockchain: State Updated
deactivate State

Blockchain -> DB: Persist Block
activate DB
DB --> Blockchain: Block Stored
deactivate DB
Blockchain --> Protocol: Block Accepted
deactivate Blockchain

Protocol -> P2P: Broadcast Block
activate P2P
P2P -> Peer: BlockResponse Message
deactivate P2P
Protocol --> Mining: Block Confirmed
deactivate Protocol
deactivate Mining

== Performance: Peer Discovery & Connection ==
P2P -> Peer: Peer Discovery Request
activate P2P
activate Peer
Peer --> P2P: Peer List
P2P -> P2P: Establish SecretConnection (NaCl)
P2P -> Protocol: Register New Peer
activate Protocol
Protocol -> Protocol: Start Reactor Event Loop
Protocol --> P2P: Peer Registered
deactivate Protocol
deactivate P2P
deactivate Peer

== Deployment: Health Check & Monitoring ==
Operator -> API: Query Node Status (gRPC)
activate API
API -> Protocol: Get Sync Status
activate Protocol
Protocol --> API: Current Height & Sync State
deactivate Protocol

API -> TxPool: Get Pool Statistics
activate TxPool
TxPool --> API: Pending Tx Count
deactivate TxPool

API -> Mining: Get Mining Stats
activate Mining
Mining --> API: Hash Rate & Block Count
deactivate Mining

API --> Operator: Node Health Report
deactivate API

@enduml
